{"info": {"author": "voilalex", "author_email": "ilya.vouk@gmail.com", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable", "Environment :: Console :: Curses", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.5", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Topic :: System :: Filesystems", "Topic :: Utilities"], "description": "# appdata | Application Data Management\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip install appdata\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nTo manage paths of application data folder there is `AppDataPaths` class:\n\n```python\nfrom appdata import AppDataPaths\n\npaths = AppDataPaths('myapp')\n```\n\nTo create the application folder tree:\n\n```python\n# `verbose` is to log the creation process\npaths.setup(verbose=True)\n```\n\nThere are few paths specified to manage your application data folder:\n\n```python\nprint(paths.app_name)  # myapp\nprint(paths.app_data_path)  # (for Linux) /home/<user>/.myapp\nprint(paths.logs_folder_path)  # (for Linux) /home/<user>/.myapp/logs\nprint(paths.main_config_path)  # (for Linux) /home/<user>/.myapp/myapp.ini\n```\n\n## Contributing\n\nSee [CONTRIBUTING.md](CONTRIBUTING.md)\n\n## License\n\n[MIT](LICENSE.md)", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "https://github.com/VoIlAlex/appdata/archive/v1.2.0.tar.gz", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/VoIlAlex/appdata", "keywords": "utils,filesystem,paths,resources", "license": "MIT", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "appdata", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/appdata/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/appdata/", "project_urls": {"Download": "https://github.com/VoIlAlex/appdata/archive/v1.2.0.tar.gz", "Homepage": "https://github.com/VoIlAlex/appdata"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/appdata/1.2.0/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": "", "summary": "Utils to manage application data folder.", "version": "1.2.0", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>appdata | Application Data Management</h1>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<pre>pip install appdata\n</pre>\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n<p>To manage paths of application data folder there is <code>AppDataPaths</code> class:</p>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">appdata</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">AppDataPaths</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">paths</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">AppDataPaths</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'myapp'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<p>To create the application folder tree:</p>\n<pre><span class=\"c1\"># `verbose` is to log the creation process</span>\n<span class=\"n\">paths</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">setup</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">verbose</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<p>There are few paths specified to manage your application data folder:</p>\n<pre><span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">paths</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">app_name</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>  <span class=\"c1\"># myapp</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">paths</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">app_data_path</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>  <span class=\"c1\"># (for Linux) /home/&lt;user&gt;/.myapp</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">paths</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">logs_folder_path</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>  <span class=\"c1\"># (for Linux) /home/&lt;user&gt;/.myapp/logs</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">paths</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">main_config_path</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>  <span class=\"c1\"># (for Linux) /home/&lt;user&gt;/.myapp/myapp.ini</span>\n</pre>\n<h2>Contributing</h2>\n<p>See <a href=\"CONTRIBUTING.md\" rel=\"nofollow\">CONTRIBUTING.md</a></p>\n<h2>License</h2>\n<p><a href=\"LICENSE.md\" rel=\"nofollow\">MIT</a></p>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 7020959, "releases": {"1.0.0": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "cfcdb1ed3f0539e2a6694cb05f738701", "sha256": "36c5a03a033b0ef96158d8b9c37b58945336cfec1da2423c201008ee5690aea3"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "appdata-1.0.0.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "cfcdb1ed3f0539e2a6694cb05f738701", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 2554, "upload_time": "2020-04-14T23:04:19", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-04-14T23:04:19.975891Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/9f/a9/55191678ed5d71db05bb37d0acff4c36670b52c8211b934cc09a6b5070b6/appdata-1.0.0.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "1.1.0": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "5dbd9af23c112ef9c25d52d59673ab6c", "sha256": "b08cf38e34cc79fd8ab12387fc793ebd5bdfe806db14b111af17f849afdef9ee"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "appdata-1.1.0.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "5dbd9af23c112ef9c25d52d59673ab6c", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 2627, "upload_time": "2020-04-14T23:32:31", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-04-14T23:32:31.790789Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/b0/e0/58d2312bf8c327e4c482f14533699fb97f78e7a62bb5e8e92f57531fa0c8/appdata-1.1.0.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "1.2.0": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "1f1bd3a888769dfebe08436cfebc0caf", "sha256": "20c0995ba5a83ea64c9a363a9d0baadaca00d4c28c3f4697064630a82b8ddc55"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "appdata-1.2.0.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "1f1bd3a888769dfebe08436cfebc0caf", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 265